{"tid":153681,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[潮汕美食]深夜分享😋","createTime":"2017-03-12T17:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T18:56:48.000Z","uid":54848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"696ea1da75380aaa6d8497d21226d447346dfc44","tid":153681,"uid":54848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hgxdlr62\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhgxdlr62&h=4caf5259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dqfc0ik9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdqfc0ik9&h=98245c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說細佬經常都要北上出差<br />\n去潮汕地區亦經常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分享下地道野,真係平靚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61015b1daa0594ce035d057605341b54495e45bb","tid":153681,"uid":54848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:32:23.000Z","msg":"電話up相頭已側<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7bd6354cbab0518091dc98782531280d749724","tid":153681,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:58:26.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"0d2fd1b1fc5c4ac8598acf3eec9ea01189b30064","tid":153681,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T18:11:11.000Z","msg":"潮州佬煮野確係有一手<br />\n鹵水海鮮牛腩粉麵"},{"pid":"77674498b32ff088faf911563b772d57eb79f3c1","tid":153681,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T18:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30fcd0c8156764d4e36a7ca60e56e1c48b4f454","tid":153681,"uid":54848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T18:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>潮州佬煮野確係有一手<br />\n鹵水海鮮牛腩粉麵</blockquote><br />\n不過呢邊既食肆真係估你唔到<br />\n唔好見佢裝修殘殘舊舊但其實好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好多時真係好似國產007咁擔住支煙整野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc101db175c6b0f5e72a391b41d922324fec1c9","tid":153681,"uid":54848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T18:22:08.000Z","msg":"講返先~<br />\n果碗野呢度叫粿條湯(其實個麵底好似河粉)<br />\n全日24小時都可以食<br />\n一般十蚊有得食,唔會超過十五蚊<br />\n材料任你配<br />\n主要係用豬什煮,另有蠔仔,肉丸,魚片頭,青口,九肚魚 都可以配<br />\n<br />\n另一碟潮式腸粉真係屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n菜,肉,蛋,再加少少豉油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd37b496402c8729ab24d019bb7287bdb958bb07","tid":153681,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:49:33.000Z","msg":"個腸粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a075f91fefb924ad5bd7ff68686c2c58c695e6d9","tid":153681,"uid":57119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"巴打 有無食鼠穀粿？<br />\n好好食架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951f649982f42aea61c1b29804c5d79368b49556","tid":153681,"uid":54848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T18:03:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 有無食鼠穀粿？<br />\n好好食架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我唔係好知咩粿同咩粿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔識聽<br />\n人地隊到埋黎就食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該食過既"},{"pid":"998945b163891a16bdbd1ac2c7c7d69d45d2d33a","tid":153681,"uid":57119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:46:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打 有無食鼠穀粿？<br />\n好好食架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我唔係好知咩粿同咩粿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔識聽<br />\n人地隊到埋黎就食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.